data.description: Absolutely stunning inside and out! This home has been kept in impeccable shape. It perfectly blends sophistication and comfort. Whitehouse ISD. Very family friendly split floor plan, that includes 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. The living room is spacious with a fireplace that opens into the kitchen. The living room has a soaring beautiful ceiling made from cedar wood. The kitchen has a large island that includes a high bronze faucet. White beautiful granite countertops cover the large island and cabinets. Kitchen cabinets are white, matching the countertops perfectly. The oversized primary bedroom has attached ensuite double vanities. The primary bedroom has a tile walk in shower along with a standalone soaking tub for maximum relaxation. For extra convenience, the primary bedroom connects directly to the laundry room. The entire downstairs flooring is covered with beautiful wood designed laminate, apart from the bedrooms and bathrooms.
